It looks like all callers have owned `OsString` values, so I think you can update them to pass the owned values and write this as:
```
fn osstring_as_utf8(path: OsString) -> Result<String, String> {
  path.into_string().or_else(|e| {
    Err(format!("{:?}'s file_name is not representable in UTF8", e))
  })
}
```
...to avoid copying.

